data.description:
Nestled in the heart of Gorham this beautifully restored 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom property is a testament to timeless elegance and modern convenience.

As you approach the home, you'll be captivated by its charming curb appeal.  The newly built wrap around porch sets the tone for the warm and inviting atmosphere that awaits inside.

Stepping through the front door, you'll find the open-concept living spaces seamlessly flow from room to room, offering a perfect blend of connectivity and privacy. 

In the kitchen, modern appliances, ample cabinetry, and granite countertops combine to create an inviting space for all. Whether you're preparing a meal for your loved ones or hosting a gathering, there is room for it all. 

Throughout the home, you'll find original hardwood flooring, tasteful finishes, and stunning stained glass windows that bathe the rooms in natural light. One large, newly renovated bedroom on the first floor allows for many options and possible multi-generational living.  The upstairs three bedrooms provide ample space for bedroom use or office space to work from home.  Both bathrooms have also been updated.

Outside, the property has a generous yard where you can unwind, play, or entertain. It's an ideal space for gardening, gathering around the fire pit or for simply enjoying the serene Maine seasons.  

The garage has been outfitted with two new garage doors.  The barn is an amazing space with so many options!   The zoning is OR for potential multi-family or office use.  The list goes on.  

To truly get an idea of what a nod to historical Gorham this house is, you have to see it in person!

OPEN HOUSE SUNDAY SEPTEMBER 23rd from 2-4
